&gt;with the tuner is required or even helps.  I found another voice towards 
&gt;the start of the same session. This is a slower talker but to my ears the 
&gt;same voice throughout. I hear a male voice and this does require some 
&gt;mental filtering of the high frequency noise. The time that the message is 
&gt;spoken is important because I would have tuned across at least half the FM 
&gt;broadcast band during the message segment.
